@startuml
title Agentic Flow v2.3.0 - Actual Run Flow (Run 4 — label-events-api)

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Team Lead" as TL
participant "Product Manager" as PM
participant "Java Architect" as ARCH
participant "Reviewer" as REV
participant "Java Coder" as CODER

note over TL,CODER #E2E8F0
Green = passed gate
Yellow = rejected / returned
Red = red card
end note

group Planning Phase [14 min, 11% context]
TL -> PM : Story request
PM -[#22C55E]> TL : Story accepted\n(<1 sec, Haiku)
TL -> ARCH : Create plan
ARCH --> TL : Plan ready\n(3 slices, 6 min, Sonnet 4.6)
TL -> REV : Phase 1 review\n(Sonnet 4.6)
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS\n(first attempt)
end

group Implementation Phase [1h 6min, 27% context]
TL -> CODER : Batch 1 (slices 1-2)\n(Codex)
CODER -[#22C55E]> TL : Batch 1 accepted\n(first clean handoff, 20 min)
note right of CODER #D1FAE5
First time Coder passed
intermediate handoff cleanly
in v2.3.0 history
end note

TL -> CODER : Batch 2 (slice 3)
CODER -[#22C55E]> TL : Batch 2 accepted\n(17 min)
end

group Verification Phase [27% context]
TL -> TL : final-check + karate\n(most context-hungry phase)
end

group Review Phase 2 [20 min, 38% context]
TL -> REV : Phase 2 review\n(Sonnet 4.6)
REV -[#F59E0B]> TL : FAIL\ncontext-map + report issues
TL -> CODER : Fix documentation
CODER --> TL : Doc fix applied\n(~5 min)
TL -> REV : Phase 2 re-check
REV -[#22C55E]> TL : PASS\n(scoped revalidation only)
note right of REV #D1FAE5
Sonnet 4.6 scoped down:
only rechecked specific findings,
not full checklist
end note
TL -[#22C55E]> TL : Final sign-off\n1h 20min, 38% context
end

@enduml
